{"tid":502532,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"DR醫學美容集團創辦人周向榮重囚12年!","createTime":"2017-12-18T03:49:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-18T14:22:45.000Z","uid":136994,"like":182,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"a0cf262ad465599203d7b85d11d231f62a093f2b","tid":502532,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T03:49:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171218/57595684\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171218%2F57595684&d=bGNBR22iDGm65AEqoHDsIDOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=c13cd8e4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171218%2F57595684&h=4be63e70\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171218/57595684</a><br />\n<br />\n2012年發生的DR醫學美容事故，集團創辦人周向榮、技術室化驗員陳冠忠嚴重疏忽誤殺罪成，法官在上周聽罷求情後，今指周向榮沒有悔意，判他入獄12年。<br />\n<br />\n陪審團未能就醫生麥允齡面對的誤殺罪達成有效裁決，控方有意申請案件重審，案件將於下月19日處理。"},{"pid":"09e190b1602f3c255d8ed770820bc180e3f7a2d2","tid":502532,"uid":389,"like":1,"dislike":15,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T03:50:26.000Z","msg":"以為美女有好報，結果"},{"pid":"efb9d15d22342393c131789f293539cb4f64a10f","tid":502532,"uid":44562,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T03:52:47.000Z","msg":"女醫生麥允齡會點 ?"},{"pid":"b804e30a02affce92afa88a2f1c4b6333f42bbcd","tid":502532,"uid":389,"like":3,"dislike":73,"score":-70,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T03:53:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>女醫生麥允齡會點 ?</blockquote><br />\n靚女，當然希望佢無事"},{"pid":"ed6b3a0d54ffc4174eecdd022675e63aa08a18f5","tid":502532,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T03:53:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5568098506b0e774f85a2b3940c34a75df1e241","tid":502532,"uid":58670,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-